{"build_type":"library","description":"Launcher wrapper whose entire body is one tail-chain launch of the universe-analysis worker. reconcile calls this as an ordinary function: the tail launch spawns the analysis worker in its own arena, awaits its single result, and returns it -- letting reconcile continue (load results) after the worker's arena is gone, without itself ending in a launch.","module_name":"run-analysis-worker-launcher","package_name":"run-analysis-worker-launcher","function_definitions":{"run-analysis-worker-launcher":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"request","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"launch_worker_binary","target_binary":"run-universe-analysis-as-tail-chain-worker","cycle_type":"tail-chain","input":"request"}]}}}